### Obtener todas las tareas
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/tareas/
Authorization: Bearer <<token>>

### 1. Registrar un nuevo usuario (POST)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/auth/registro/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "dannasofiamp02@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456789",
    "rol":"instructor"
}

### 2. Iniciar sesión (POST)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "dannasofiamp02@gmail.com",
    "password": "123456789"
}
### 3. Crear una nueva tarea (POST)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/tareas/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <<TOKEN>>
{
    "titulo": "Tarea con API Segura",
    "descripcion": "Mi primera tarea usuando JWT de Firebase"
}
### ELIMINAR TODAS LAS TAREAS (SOLO INSTRUCTOR)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/tareas/
Authorization: Bearer <<TOKEN_DEL_INSTRUCTOR>>

### ELIMINAR UNA TAREA POR ID
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/api_tareas/tareas/ID_DE_LA_TAREA/
Authorization: Bearer <<TOKEN>>

